DzQuickToggle
=============

Quick toggle light switches on your home screen for Domoticz


Description
-----------

DzQuickToggle allows you to add toggle switches to your Android home
screen (launcher) for any lights you have configured in your Domoticz
smart home.

Note: Only anonymous authentication is currently supported.

When first starting the app, make sure to configure the URL of your
Domoticz server.


